description.plain: EST Gee is a 27-year-old American rapper from Louisville, Kentucky. Gee signed with Yo Gotti’s label CMG Records in January of 2021. His first album on CMG, Bigger Than Life Or Death, was released in July 2021. EST Gee has also collaborated extensively with fellow Louisville artist Jack Harlow.
